          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-4f0fa997afd9549a",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "$5/month\nIf you think you might frequently be going into overdraft, consider this plan. For just one low monthly fee, you can protect yourself from overage charges no matter how many times you use it\u00a0as long as the overdrawn balance is within the overdraft limit.\nIn addition, interest is also payable on overdrawn balances, calculated daily at 21% (per annum), charged monthly.\nNote : Effective\u00a0August 7, 2025, this fee is not applicable to Quebec residents.",
